Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.12,0:06:26.68,1080CN,,0,0,0,,来保持身体水量，这个过程叫血管收缩。这会导致肾血流量
Dialogue: 2,0:06:21.12,0:06:26.68,1080EN,,0,0,0,,vessels in an attempt to conserve body water. This is called vasoconstriction. This can damage the kidneys as renal
