Dialogue: 2,0:06:26.68,0:06:31.44,1080EN,,0,0,0,,perfusion is decreased. There's less blood going to the kidneys so less oxygen is getting to the tissue which
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.44,0:06:37.09,1080CN,,0,0,0,,细胞就坏死了。还有一个麻烦，现在肌肉细胞差不多该吸水涨破了
Dialogue: 2,0:06:31.44,0:06:37.09,1080EN,,0,0,0,,can cause cell death. But here's another problem, now that the muscle cells are starting to rupture, they're releasing
