Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.21,0:07:46.84,1080CN,,0,0,0,,我们称这个过程叫急性肾损伤。而深色的尿液是因为肌红蛋白含有血红素
Dialogue: 2,0:07:40.21,0:07:46.84,1080EN,,0,0,0,,of this strainer. We call this acute kidney injury. The reddish brown urine is because myoglobin contains heme
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.84,0:07:51.91,1080CN,,0,0,0,,是一种含铁的化合物，而铁与氧气作用使你的血液变红。
Dialogue: 2,0:07:46.84,0:07:51.91,1080EN,,0,0,0,,a compound that has iron that's responsible for making your blood red when exposed to oxygen. The myoglobin
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.91,0:07:56.95,1080CN,,0,0,0,,肌红蛋白积累在肾单位内，使管腔破裂，溢出进入尿液
